      <memberdef kind="function" id="_m_i_e_s___logging_8ipf_1a13a54cf6fd9396160720c21ba9a9e984" prot="public" static="no" const="no" explicit="no" inline="no" virt="non-virtual">
        <type>variable</type>
        <definition>variable LOG_AddEntry</definition>
        <argsstring>(string package, string action, WaveText keys=defaultValue, WaveText values=defaultValue)</argsstring>
        <name>LOG_AddEntry</name>
        <param>
          <type>string</type>
          <declname>package</declname>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>string</type>
          <declname>action</declname>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>WaveText</type>
          <declname>keys</declname>
          <defval>defaultValue</defval>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>WaveText</type>
          <declname>values</declname>
          <defval>defaultValue</defval>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Add entry for the current function into the log file. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Usage: <verbatim>embed:rst:leading-asterisk
*  .. code-block:: igorpro
* 
*      Function DoWork()
* 
*          LOG_AddEntry(&quot;my package&quot;, &quot;start&quot;)
* 
*          // ...
* 
*          LOG_AddEntry(&quot;my package&quot;, &quot;end&quot;)
*      End
*  </verbatim></para>
<para>Result: <verbatim>embed:rst:leading-asterisk
*  .. code-block:: js
* 
*     {&quot;action&quot;:&quot;start&quot;,&quot;exp&quot;:&quot;HardwareTests&quot;,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;DoWork&quot;,&quot;ts&quot;:&quot;2021-03-09T17:20:10.252+01:00&quot;}
*     {&quot;action&quot;:&quot;end&quot;,&quot;exp&quot;:&quot;HardwareTests&quot;,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;DoWork&quot;,&quot;ts&quot;:&quot;2021-03-09T17:20:10.298+01:00&quot;}
* 
*  </verbatim></para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>package</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>package name, this determines the log file </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>action</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>additional string, can be something like <computeroutput>start</computeroutput> or <computeroutput>end</computeroutput> </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>keys</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>[optional, defaults to $&quot;&quot;] Additional key-value pairs to be written into the log file. Same size as values. Either both <computeroutput>keys</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>values</computeroutput> are present or none. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>values</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>[optional, defaults to $&quot;&quot;] Additional key-value pairs to be written into the log file. Same size as keys. Either both <computeroutput>keys</computeroutput> and <computeroutput>values</computeroutput> are present or none. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
